00:22:00.092 --> 00:22:04.085
tsum, tsum roytn armey? tsum, tsu zayn a...?

00:22:01.695 --> 00:22:04.507
 ya, tsu zayn a s- a guter soldat.

00:22:05.897 --> 00:22:07.409
nu, ikh hob opgedint

00:22:08.007 --> 00:22:09.249
dray yor,

00:22:09.947 --> 00:22:11.949
biz tsum akht un fertsikstn yor.

00:22:12.192 --> 00:22:16.118
 ober gedint, kemfn hot ir nisht gedint?,

00:22:16.528 --> 00:22:20.909
bay, bay shiseray un baym kemfn vi a soldat hot ir nisht?

00:22:19.279 --> 00:22:23.205
ah, bay ⟨k-⟩ neyn, neyn, vayle m'hot undz nit geshikt. az me volt geshikt,

00:22:23.413 --> 00:22:27.139
volt ikh efsher gedarft geyn. mir zaynen gevezn derbay lebn Dantsig.

00:22:27.139 --> 00:22:29.752
nor undz hot men nit geshikt; ikh bin nit gegangen.

00:22:29.961 --> 00:22:33.397
un vu iz ayer tate geven? UNK mit aykh di gantse tsayt?

00:22:30.239 --> 00:22:31.239
UNK

00:22:32.053 --> 00:22:35.860
der tate iz gevezn oykhet vu, ober ikh veys nit.

00:22:35.547 --> 00:22:36.300
uhuh.

00:22:36.188 --> 00:22:37.363
kh'veys nit. er iz ge-...

00:22:37.538 --> 00:22:39.624
ikh hob getrofn im...

00:22:42.904 --> 00:22:44.822
⟨vu⟩ hob ikh im ya getrofn?

00:22:44.828 --> 00:22:45.716
neyn.

00:22:46.566 --> 00:22:49.598
ikh hob ⟨im⟩ nit getrofn. dem onkl hob ikh gehat getrofn

00:22:49.598 --> 00:22:50.644
unter vegs,

00:22:50.650 --> 00:22:52.534
ven mir zaynen gegangen

00:22:54.463 --> 00:22:55.775
epes tsu a ⟨POKH-⟩

00:22:55.775 --> 00:22:58.570
vu nit iz zaynen mir gegangen un ikh hob im gezen.

00:22:58.800 --> 00:23:01.848
un nokh eyner a mentsh hot gez- Baytler

00:23:01.855 --> 00:23:03.604
hot oykhet mir gezen,

00:23:04.487 --> 00:23:08.753
un er hot ibergegebn mayn mamen. zi iz gekumen fun

00:23:08.753 --> 00:23:11.681
evakuatsye, fun vu zi iz gevezn, fun

00:23:11.681 --> 00:23:13.796
CHEBOKSARY, fun Rusland.

00:23:13.870 --> 00:23:17.334
mit di tsvey kinder iz zi gekumen oyf tsurik in Rige.

00:23:17.334 --> 00:23:20.259
⟨ot er⟩ hot gezogt az er hot mir gezen,

00:23:20.991 --> 00:23:22.537
zayendik in armey,

00:23:22.712 --> 00:23:23.988
az ikh leb,

00:23:25.108 --> 00:23:26.334
un ikh din.

00:23:26.560 --> 00:23:28.106
ikh bin in armey.

00:23:28.129 --> 00:23:30.992
⟨vi, z-⟩ dertseyl vi azoy ir hot,

00:23:32.348 --> 00:23:33.678
ir zayt ts-,

00:23:33.678 --> 00:23:36.508
tsuzamengekumen mit ayer mame un

00:23:36.508 --> 00:23:39.547
mit ayer tate nokh a mol, un mit ayere brider,

00:23:39.570 --> 00:23:43.445
un nemt undz tsu der tsayt vos ir hot zikh bakent mit ayer froy.

00:23:48.328 --> 00:23:50.397
di ershte zakh iz,

00:23:50.597 --> 00:23:54.579
v- ven hob ikh gekrogn d- fun vu, vi hob ikh gevust

00:23:54.579 --> 00:23:56.417
di, az zey l- z- lebn?

00:23:56.417 --> 00:23:58.577
ikh hob dokh getrakht di gantse tsayt,

00:23:58.577 --> 00:24:01.806
⟨iz⟩, zaynen zey lebn oder, zey lebn oder zey lebn nit?

00:24:02.200 --> 00:24:04.050
iz, forndik...

00:24:04.174 --> 00:24:07.222
mir zaynen geforn fun Daytshland in Krim.

00:24:08.494 --> 00:24:10.448
in Krim, in di,

00:24:10.448 --> 00:24:12.116
in poyezd.

00:24:13.202 --> 00:24:15.896
mit a mol, der, der vos trogt

00:24:15.919 --> 00:24:19.864
di briv, di potsh- di briv,

00:24:19.864 --> 00:24:21.954
⟨POCH- nu⟩, di potsht, di briv,

00:24:22.112 --> 00:24:23.810
ruft oys mayn nomen.

00:24:25.909 --> 00:24:28.485
zog ikh nokh tsu im, "du lakhst fun mir.

00:24:28.795 --> 00:24:30.732
s'ken nit zayn az ikh zol hobn

00:24:30.732 --> 00:24:32.569
fun vemen tsu krign a briv."

00:24:32.777 --> 00:24:35.268
zogt er, "neyn, dos iz far dir a briv."

00:24:35.443 --> 00:24:38.255
un ikh nem di briv, un dos hot mayn bruder,

00:24:39.409 --> 00:24:41.529
der tsveyter bruder, geshribn.

00:24:41.974 --> 00:24:45.101
vayle oyf vifl Baytler hot im gezogt...

00:24:45.101 --> 00:24:46.839
un er iz oykhet gevezn,

00:24:46.839 --> 00:24:48.291
er hot zikh mobil-,

00:24:48.291 --> 00:24:51.305
er iz shoyn gegangen aheym. er iz oykh gevezn in armey,

00:24:51.305 --> 00:24:52.498
hot er gevust

00:24:53.061 --> 00:24:57.031
in vos far a, polk, nu, vos far a,

00:24:57.031 --> 00:24:58.488
vu ikh din.

00:24:59.102 --> 00:25:01.233
hot er gegebn dem adres,

00:25:01.233 --> 00:25:02.302
mit dem

00:25:02.663 --> 00:25:05.216
⟨PO-⟩ vi heyst UNK? a spetsyel,

00:25:05.216 --> 00:25:07.415
spetsyeler numer,

00:25:07.827 --> 00:25:11.899
un di briv iz ongekumen. ot dan ⟨hob es,⟩ hob ikh dervust zikh az

00:25:11.899 --> 00:25:13.510
zey zaynen lebn geblibn,

00:25:13.510 --> 00:25:15.701
di mame mit di tsvey brider.

00:25:15.927 --> 00:25:18.705
un der tate hot zey, hot zey gefunen?

00:25:18.475 --> 00:25:21.135
un der tate hot zey gefunen, ya, gekumen...

00:25:19.673 --> 00:25:21.607
er iz tsurikgeforn keyn Rige?

00:25:21.847 --> 00:25:24.898
⟨, az zey,⟩ ya, in Rige, az zey zaynen shoyn gevezn in Rige,

00:25:25.157 --> 00:25:26.904
vayle UNK...

00:25:25.225 --> 00:25:30.332
ven iz dos geven az ir hot zikh dervust vegn der mamen un di b- di brider?

00:25:30.827 --> 00:25:33.757
ven ir hot bakumen dem briv, ven iz dos geven?

00:25:33.207 --> 00:25:38.314
nu, dos iz gevezn, mir zaynen geforn shoyn fun Daytshland. dos iz shoyn gevezn in,

00:25:38.860 --> 00:25:41.469
in zeks un fertsikstn yor.

00:25:41.492 --> 00:25:43.376
zeks un fertsikstn yor.

00:25:44.243 --> 00:25:47.747
mir zaynen geforn in Krim. dortn hob ikh nokh tsvey yor gedint.

00:25:47.803 --> 00:25:51.003
far vos hot ayer tate nisht gevust in velkhe

00:25:51.094 --> 00:25:52.725
polk ir, ir dint?

00:25:52.292 --> 00:25:55.323
e- vayl er iz, mir dakht zikh, nit gevezn in armey.

00:25:56.005 --> 00:25:58.007
kh'veys nit vos er hot geton.

00:25:56.578 --> 00:26:00.672
ober ir, ir hot zikh tsesheydt fun im? ir hot nisht gehat keyn kontakt mit im?

00:25:59.481 --> 00:26:02.605
neyn, mir hobn keyn kontakt nit gehat. er iz dokh avek,

00:26:02.605 --> 00:26:04.612
ven m'hot undz damolst tsesheydt,

00:26:04.612 --> 00:26:07.920
iz er avek mit an ander g- grupe mentshn.

00:26:06.161 --> 00:26:06.745
uhuh.

00:26:07.446 --> 00:26:10.612
vi azoy hot er gefunen di vayb mit di kinder?

00:26:10.213 --> 00:26:14.037
vayle er hot dokh, in Rige hot er dokh gevust, ⟨i-⟩ in Rige,

00:26:11.682 --> 00:26:13.633
in Rige, ⟨in Rige⟩.

00:26:14.213 --> 00:26:17.244
⟨,⟩ hot er gevust. er iz gegangen ⟨a-⟩...

00:26:15.180 --> 00:26:16.180
⟨⟩.

00:26:16.180 --> 00:26:21.930
iz, er hot, er hot geveyst az du blaybs- er hot gevust az d- az ir blaybt lebn, ober

00:26:21.930 --> 00:26:23.589
er hot nisht gevust vu ir zayt?

00:26:22.060 --> 00:26:27.009
er hot nit ge- er hot nit gevust. er, er hot dervust zikh oykhet fun Baytler.

00:26:27.009 --> 00:26:28.517
ot der Baytler

00:26:27.427 --> 00:26:28.220
⟨a⟩.

00:26:28.590 --> 00:26:29.849
hot gezogt,

00:26:30.109 --> 00:26:31.892
vayle er hot mir oykh nit gezen.

00:26:31.999 --> 00:26:34.256
er hot aykh nisht gezen baym sof?

00:26:32.826 --> 00:26:35.867
⟨ya⟩, er hot mir... neyn, tsum letst hot er mir shoyn nit gezen,

00:26:35.867 --> 00:26:38.715
nor Baytler hot im gezogt az er hot mir gezen

00:26:38.715 --> 00:26:39.772
un ikh din.

00:26:40.033 --> 00:26:42.983
 un ayer froy, vos iz...?

00:26:42.192 --> 00:26:46.576
nu, dos, nokh dem bin ikh shoyn in akht un fertsikstn yor, az ikh hob zikh shoyn

00:26:46.576 --> 00:26:47.805
oysgedint,

00:26:48.975 --> 00:26:50.994
bin ikh gekumen oykh in Rige.

00:26:52.603 --> 00:26:58.551
bin gekumen in Rige, hob ikh gefunen di mamen. kh'hob gefunen dem bruder, dem tsveytn bruder.

00:26:58.551 --> 00:27:02.436
kh'hob gefunen mayne k- mayn tanten, dem kuz⟨ang⟩,

00:27:02.577 --> 00:27:03.938
dem onkl,

00:27:04.450 --> 00:27:05.692
der tate,

00:27:07.707 --> 00:27:10.030
dem onkl vos iz gevezn in,

00:27:10.795 --> 00:27:14.287
nu, keg- vos gekemft kegn di daytshn.

00:27:15.807 --> 00:27:20.363
nu, un di mame zogt,... un ikh hob shoyn getrakht az me darf,

00:27:20.818 --> 00:27:23.090
UNK nokh durkhtsulebn aza min lebn,

00:27:23.350 --> 00:27:26.011
darf men lebn a mentshishn lebn.

00:27:26.995 --> 00:27:30.796
me darf khasene hobn, nu, ya.

00:27:31.382 --> 00:27:33.502
kh'hob nit gevelt shoyn keyn ander lebn.

00:27:33.863 --> 00:27:35.426
nu, hot mir mayn mame

00:27:38.520 --> 00:27:41.593
bakent gemakht... zey zaynen dokh gevezn,

00:27:41.912 --> 00:27:43.530
di mames,

00:27:43.954 --> 00:27:45.382
hobn zikh gekent?

00:27:44.646 --> 00:27:48.302
UNK tsuzamen... bakent gemakht mit ir,

00:27:49.185 --> 00:27:52.520
un mir hobn khasene gehat in akht un fertsikstn yor.

00:27:54.298 --> 00:27:56.941
dos, vifl bin ikh gevezn? ikh bin gekumen in

00:27:57.319 --> 00:27:58.865
mart monat,

00:27:59.108 --> 00:28:01.130
un in SENTA- in SENTYABR,

00:28:01.130 --> 00:28:02.376
in september

00:28:03.057 --> 00:28:04.772
hob ikh shoyn khasene gehat.

00:28:06.820 --> 00:28:08.417
un gehat a,

00:28:09.875 --> 00:28:11.150
⟨⟩,

00:28:11.173 --> 00:28:13.630
a mishpokhe dort, mit kinder?

00:28:12.793 --> 00:28:16.058
ya, tsvey kinder: a zun

00:28:16.058 --> 00:28:17.377
mit a tokhter,

00:28:17.164 --> 00:28:18.575
un zey heysn?

00:28:19.341 --> 00:28:21.866
un yetst hob ikh, ⟨he⟩, fir eyniklekh.

00:28:21.822 --> 00:28:24.094
di, di zun un di tokhter heysn?

00:28:24.057 --> 00:28:26.951
di tokhter iz MARINA, ⟨vet⟩ zi bald kumen,

00:28:27.103 --> 00:28:28.329
un der zun?

00:28:27.424 --> 00:28:29.123
un der zun heyst

00:28:29.123 --> 00:28:30.203
Borukh.

00:28:30.244 --> 00:28:30.968
Borekh.

00:28:30.985 --> 00:28:32.241
Borukh.

00:28:32.241 --> 00:28:35.521
un ale, der zun iz a gemalter,

00:28:36.013 --> 00:28:37.588
di eyniklekh zaynen ale

00:28:37.588 --> 00:28:40.512
⟨l- nit⟩ lebndik dortn, afile in Rusland,

00:28:41.228 --> 00:28:43.955
hobn mir gemalt dem eynikl oykhet.

00:28:45.852 --> 00:28:47.196
⟨i⟩n di zakhn...

00:28:47.640 --> 00:28:50.919
mir hobn nit keyn groyse, mir hobn moyre,

00:28:50.919 --> 00:28:54.080
m⟨ir⟩, opgelebt a lebn, ober ikh'l nit zogn az ikh,

00:28:54.627 --> 00:28:57.153
ikh hob far vos moyre gehat.

00:29:00.415 --> 00:29:02.214
az me darf, flegn mir ton.

00:29:02.980 --> 00:29:04.729
nor durkhtsulebn dem,

00:29:06.490 --> 00:29:09.032
dem lebn vos kh'hob durkhgelebt bayn daytsh,

00:29:09.865 --> 00:29:12.643
iz, iz, iz, bashtimt

00:29:12.717 --> 00:29:14.905
iz nito vos moyre tsu hobn,

00:29:15.130 --> 00:29:16.963
vayle dortn bin ikh shoyn

00:29:17.205 --> 00:29:18.819
gevezn nit eyn mol

00:29:19.433 --> 00:29:20.675
oyf yener velt.

00:29:21.205 --> 00:29:22.802
o, es MIGAET vider.

00:29:22.909 --> 00:29:25.552
yo, lomir baytn di, tashmes un,

00:29:25.778 --> 00:29:27.012
 un geyn vayter.
